textAfterTable: * Note from Moshe Kutten: My grandfather Shmuel Edelstein, his wife (my grandmother) Yossefa Edelstein (Apter) and their kids (my aunt and uncle) Fridle- Zigfrid Edlestein and Edith Edlestein perished in Stryj or in Belzec camp. I have pictures of all of them.
